The paper discusses the evaluation of generative models, with a particular emphasis on GANs. This topic is highly relevant to the sub-field of machine learning known as "deep learning" (cs.LG), as well as computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses measures related to neural networks (cs.NE) and graph theory (cs.GR), which are also relevant to the evaluation of GANs.
